data.description:
NO CATS. Other pets with owner approval and additional deposit/rent.Convenient commute location with hiking trails in the neighborhood. This gorgeous 3 bedroom home has views of the mountains and, when they're out playing, the Northern Lights from its many large windows. Modern kitchen with all stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops and pantry. Features 2 living areas. Cozy up by the natural gas fireplace downstairs or relax in the soaking tub in the private bathroom upstairs. Laundry room located upstairs. 3 car, oversized heated garage with paved driveway and RV parking/hookups on the side of the building. Huge open landscaped backyard with beautiful deck.

Renter is responsible for Trash, Electric, Gas, Water. Lease duration minimum of 12 months out to 36 months. Tenant responsible for lawn care and snow removal. Pets are with owner approval with additional pet deposit/rent and no cats are allowed.
